### 1. Dynamic Locator Synthesis & Healing
* **Contextual DOM Extraction:** Captures localized components along with accessibility parameters to calculate stable Playwright user-facing semantic selectors (like getByRole and getByLabel).
* **Self-Healing Selectors:** Automatically intercepts runtime TimeoutException errors, parses the updated UI state, and applies real-time locator repairs.

### 2. Autonomous Test Case Generation
* **Gherkin-to-Code Mapping:** Scans .feature text requirements and constructs isolated, executable Playwright step definitions using your project's active TestContext model.
* **Boundary & Negative Input Injections:** Analyzes input forms dynamically to insert boundary limits, invalid parameters, and negative edge cases.

### 3. Smart Execution Control & Flaky Test Triaging
* **Intelligent Retry Analysis:** Evaluates error streams to isolate infrastructure/network environment drops from true application state crashes.
* **Dynamic Synchronization Engine:** Intercepts timing failures and substitutes arbitrary hardcoded timeouts with state-driven conditional checks.